590
00:37:33,967 --> 00:37:35,533
But I've forgotten.

591
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:37,767
I've forgotten, I've forgotten.

592
00:37:37,833 --> 00:37:40,633
We forget without trying.

593
00:37:42,067 --> 00:37:43,933
Why did I walk over here just now?

594
